    summary: "From October this year Samsung will roll out a variety of new paid tiers for access to its SmartThings API, including a $4.99 monthly plan for \"non-commercial, individual developers.\" It won't just be developers that pay the price though. Some more advanced smart home users are likely to fall afoul of the rule change if [&#8230;]",
